What is enegery harvesting meaning ?

Harvesting = අස්වනු 
Energy = බලශක්තිය

Energy which derived from external soruces , like ; wind, solar, kinetic, thermal , radio etc..

Basic Concept: 

Energy harvesting ---> Stored in (Capcitor) (Low energy) ------> releasing energy 
Example for the application: 

Enerfy Harvesting ---> stored ----> low power microcontroller -- > I/O Control 






